<%
  set_seo_meta(
    title: "Disclaimer - BizBlasts",
    description: "Important disclaimers about the BizBlasts platform, the content on sites we host, and the goods and services sold by independent businesses through BizBlasts.",
    canonical: "https://www.bizblasts.com/disclaimer"
  )

  effective_date = "June 1, 2026"
  support_email  = ENV.fetch('SUPPORT_EMAIL', 'bizblaststeam@gmail.com')
%>

<%= render layout: 'shared/legal_page',
           locals: {
             eyebrow: 'Disclaimer',
             title: 'Disclaimer',
             summary: "Important context about the BizBlasts platform, the content on sites we host for independent businesses, and what we are and are not responsible for.",
             effective_date: effective_date,
             contact_email: support_email
           } do %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '1. General Information Only' } do %>
    <p>
      The information published on BizBlasts and on sites we host is provided for general informational
      purposes only. It is not professional advice (legal, medical, financial, tax, accounting, or
      otherwise), and you should not rely on it as a substitute for advice from a qualified professional in
      the relevant field.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '2. Independent Businesses' } do %>
    <p>
      Many sites that look and behave like normal business websites are hosted by independent businesses
      using BizBlasts. The business is responsible for its own pricing, availability, scheduling, services,
      products, claims, reviews, and customer communications. BizBlasts does not provide those services, set
      those prices, or vet every claim made by every business that uses the platform.
    </p>
    <p>
      When you book, purchase, or communicate through a BizBlasts-hosted site, you are entering into a
      transaction or relationship with the underlying business, not with BizBlasts.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '3. No Endorsement' } do %>
    <p>
      The presence of a business, service, product, review, or third-party link on BizBlasts or on a
      BizBlasts-hosted site does not constitute an endorsement, certification, or recommendation by
      BizBlasts. Reviews displayed via integrations (such as Google reviews) are produced by their original
      authors and providers; BizBlasts does not author or verify them.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '4. Forward-Looking Statements and Estimates' } do %>
    <p>
      Pricing estimates, service-area estimates, availability windows, projected arrival or completion times,
      and similar forward-looking information are estimates only and may change. Actual results, including
      whether a service can be performed, how long it will take, and what it will cost, depend on factors
      outside our control.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '5. AI-Generated and Automated Content' } do %>
    <p>
      Portions of the platform may use automated tools or AI models to draft content, summarize
      conversations, suggest responses, or assist with workflows. Automated output may be incomplete,
      inaccurate, biased, or inappropriate for a given context. You should review automated output before
      relying on it for important decisions or communications.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '6. External Links and Third-Party Services' } do %>
    <p>
      BizBlasts and BizBlasts-hosted sites may link to or integrate with third-party websites and services
      (such as map providers, review platforms, payment processors, calendar systems, and analytics
      providers). We do not control those third parties and are not responsible for their content, privacy
      practices, availability, or terms.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '7. No Warranties' } do %>
    <p>
      The platform, its content, and the sites we host are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; and &ldquo;as
      available,&rdquo; without warranty of any kind. To the maximum extent permitted by law, BizBlasts
      disclaims all warranties, express or implied, including warranties of merchantability, fitness for a
      particular purpose, accuracy, and non-infringement.
    </p>
    <p>
      We do not warrant that the platform will be uninterrupted, error-free, or completely secure, that any
      particular bookings or sales will be realized, or that any particular search-ranking, deliverability,
      or domain-verification outcome will occur.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '8. Limitation of Liability' } do %>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by law, BizBlasts and its affiliates, officers, employees, and agents
      will not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, special, exemplary, or punitive
      damages arising out of or relating to your use of the platform or any content on it, including any
      decisions you make based on that content.
    </p>
    <p>
      For a more detailed allocation of risk, including the cap on our total liability, see our
      <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: 'text-primary hover:underline' %>.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '9. Changes' } do %>
    <p>
      We may update this Disclaimer from time to time by posting a revised version on the site and updating
      the effective date above.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <%= render layout: 'shared/legal_section', locals: { title: '10. Contact' } do %>
    <p>
      Questions about this Disclaimer may be sent to
      <%= mail_to support_email, support_email, class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>.
    </p>
  <% end %>

<% end %>
